name: Dan Collins Design
overview:
Daniel Collins Design has cultivated a reputation for being dependable, successful and tireless in the use of design as a strategic tool in business. Effective design can create desire, impact productivity, initiate change, and clarify the complex. Simply put, effective design can solve any communication problem.

Specializing in creative print design, functional websites, and distinguished brand identities for over fifteen years, DCD is driven by a passion for useful, yet simplified design. An exceptional level of design skill and conceptual problem-solving have been the foundation for a portfolio of award-winning work with a strict attention to simplicity, quality and clarity of message.
